(c) an analysis of the results of the Environmental Risk Assessment, including identification of risks requiring particular focus, including in the Environmental Management and Monitoring Plan;

(d) identification of measures to monitor [Environmental Impacts and] Environmental Effects to identify measures to prevent, Mitigate and manage such [impacts,] effects and risks to as low as reasonably practicable, while within acceptable levels in accordance with environmental Standards;

